data.description: This beautiful Highland home is the same floor plan as the model home in the community!!  This masterfully built one-story home in cul de sac on an oversized lot has 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 Full baths and a study. The kitchen features grey cabinets, high ceilings, solid surface countertops, gas range with vent-a-hood, undermount sink, stainless appliances, an extended island with bar stool seating, gas cooking, plenty of cabinet space, and a walk-in pantry. This open concept Highland home connects both the family room and the breakfast area for easy entertaining. The primary suite features a large full bath, two separate vanities, a walk-in shower, separate tub, and walk-in closet. The yard is fully landscaped with a sprinkler system, with a covered patio. This home is pre-plumbed for a water softener. Buy yourself the ultimate gift this season!
